<div id="company">
  <%#= render 'pages/company-wrappers/hero' %>
  <section id="slide-1" class="wrapper hero company homeSlide">
    <div class="bcg"
      data-center="background-position: 50% 0px;"
      data-top-bottom="background-position: 50% -500px;"
      data-anchor-target="#slide-1" >
      <%= render 'layouts/wrappers/header' %>
      <div class="hsContainer">
        <div class="hsContent content"
          data-center="opacity: 1"
          data-60-top="opacity: 0"
          data-anchor-target="#slide-1 h1" >
          <section class="flex-container">
            <div class="flex-column">
              <h1>we help the
                <span class="helighted">world's </span> top
                <span class="helighted">companies</span> build
                <span class="helighted">amazing</span> digital
                <span class="helighted">products</span>
              </h1>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div><!-- content -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- hero  company -->

  <section id="slide-2" class="wrapper intro">
    <div class="bcg"
      data-0="background-color:rgb(225,225,225);"
      data-top="background-color:(225,225,225);"
      data-anchor-target="#slide-2" >
        <div class="hsContainer">
          <div class="hsContent">
            <h1
              data--0-bottom="opacity: 0"
              data--30-bottom="opacity: 1"
              data-center="opacity: 1"
              data-anchor-target="#slide-2 h1">
              <section class="flex-container align-center">
                <div class="flex-column twelve medium-four header">
                  <h1>We view ‘business’ differently at RSG.</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-column twelve medium-eight details">
                  <p>RSG Nordic AB, with offices in Gothenburg and Stockholm, Sweden, is a consultant company specialized in corporate/company and project management assignments.</p>
                  <p>Our competency ranges from general management, organizational issues, business development, supply chain management and optimizing business processes (with or without IT support) to more specific areas such as how to integrate web-based transactions into the business.</p>
                </div>
              </section>
            </h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--   <div class="divider"></div> -->

  <section id="slide-3" class="wrapper action homeSlide" style="height: 600px;">
    <div class="bcg"
      data-bottom-top="background-position: 0px 100px;"
      data-top-bottom="background-position: 0px -500px;"
      data-top-bottom="background-position: -40px 50%;"
      data-anchor-target="#slide-3"
    >
      <div class="hsContainer">
        <div class="hsContent">
          <div class="plaxEl"
            data-100-bottom="opacity: 0"
            data-bottom="opacity: 1;"
            data-anchor-target="#slide-3"
          >
            <section class="flex-container align-center">
              <div class="flex-column twelve title-area filter">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <div class="separator">
                  <i class="fa fa-sort fa-rotate-90" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                </div>
                <p>To democratize live video broadcasting and provide the tools to bring every event live online.</p>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- action -->

  <article class="section wrapper services">
    <section class="flex-container align-center header title-area">
      <h1>Our services</h1>
      <div class="separator">✻</div>
      <p>Few of our typical assignments</p>
    </section>

    <section class="flex-container service">

      <div class="flex-column twelve large-six">
        <figure class="icon ts">
          <i class="fa fa-line-chart fa-border"></i>
          <figcaption>
            <h2>Organization analysis &amp; proposed improvements</h2>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <p>In connection with e.g. introduction of new technology or revised business processes, the organization often needs to be revised as well. We have long experience from reviewing, proposing, implementing and setting up the required training for such revamped organizations.
        <br><br>
        We have also carried out mapping of business processes for a large number of companies and proposed the optimum IT tools to support these processes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-column twelve large-six">
        <figure class="icon fs">
          <i class="fa fa-cogs fa-border"></i>
          <figcaption>
            <h2>Project Management</h2>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <p>We are ready to take responsibility of managing your projects. We have acted as Project Managers for several industries ranging from IT &amp; Telecom, Energy Production, Raw Materials Management to Pulp &amp; Paper.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-column twelve large-six">
        <figure class="icon os">
          <i class="fa fa-tasks fa-border"></i>
          <figcaption>
            <h2>Evaluation of business plans</h2>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <p>As part of support to both start-ups and due diligence phases at mergers &amp; acquisitions of larger companies, we have evaluated over 100 business plans. We have also worked with our clients to improve these plans along with refining the businesses themselves.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-column twelve large-six">
        <figure class="icon ss">
          <i class="fa fa-cubes fa-border"></i>
          <figcaption>
            <h2>Procurement / Supply Management</h2>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <p>We have in-depth knowledge of local and international procurement activities, processes and contracts for equipment as well as services. For multi-national clients we have also developed &amp; executed plans for strategic sourcing of new suppliers in cost-competitive countries.<p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
